  <Summary>Martine Bancroft is Michael Morbius’ first love… but this romance threatens to end in a pool of blood.

"And What of a Vampire's Blood" continues the storyline wherein Morbius the Living Vampire finds himself caught in the conflict between Daemond the sorcerer and the Caretakers from Arcturus, with the life of Martine at stake. Will the power of the enigmatic child Tara be enough to help? Blade appears in a flashback sequence.

"The Faceless Ones" reprints an old Atlas story in which astronauts appear to make contact with a new alien race.

A Marvel Value Stamp is also contained in this issue, featuring Hela.</Summary>
